"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-8-1-viral-olympic-shooters-yusuf-dikec-and-kim-ye-ji-unfazed-by-internet-storm\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hands-in-pocket Turkish shooter Dikec and South Korea's 'sci-fi assassin' Kim have brushed aside their fame.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 42, \"end\": 53, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999877661955728, \"rank\": 1.2152266524190365e-05, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Turkish Olympic shooting medallist Yusuf Dikec says he is unfazed by his newfound fame after his casual style with no headwear and a hand in his pocket made him an overnight internet sensation.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.999994109544855, \"rank\": 5.357487205117638e-06, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dikec and partner Sevval Ilayda Tarhan won silver on Tuesday in the mixed team 10-metre (10.9-yard) air pistol, losing to Serbia in the gold medal match.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9987131935048462, \"rank\": 0.001231897779872658, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was Dikec's posture that caught attention as much as the result.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The marksman wore standard glasses, a team T-shirt and had his left hand casually slung in his pocket.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Other than his pistol, he notably had none of the specialised equipment used by athletes in the hyperprecise event like headphones, special lenses or a hat.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Be cool like Yusuf Dikec.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.999994109544855, \"rank\": 5.357487205117638e-06, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations on winning the silver medal in such a cool way,\\\" France's embassy in Turkey wrote in a post on X in Turkish.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8673376140416887, \"rank\": 0.14389666780436466, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999727168399019, \"rank\": 2.704014803567729e-05, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"score\": 0.8167092016559128, \"rank\": 0.2234577480602302, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The name's Dikec.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yusuf Dikec,\\\" said posts by other users in reference to cinema icon James Bond.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.999994109544855, \"rank\": 5.357487205117638e-06, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Bond\", \"score\": 0.9999988613619396, \"rank\": 1.1386393094662882e-06, \"text\": \"James Bond\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Bond\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Bond\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some memes added a cigarette to his mouth to emphasise the relaxed posture.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to Turkish channel TGRT Haber, Dikec acknowledged he had adopted the rare technique of shooting with both eyes open whereas most athletes keep one closed or obscured.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"score\": 0.8167092016559128, \"rank\": 0.2234577480602302, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGRT_Haber\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGRT Haber\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGRT_Haber\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGRT_Haber\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My shooting technique is one of the rare shooting techniques in the world.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I shoot with both eyes open.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the referees are surprised by this,\\\" he said on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said winning a medal was no surprise because \\\"this year we prepared a lot and worked a lot.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 This success belongs to all of Turkey.\\\"\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"score\": 0.9999727168399019, \"rank\": 2.704014803567729e-05, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Success does not come with your hands in your pockets.\\\"\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some social media users suggested equal attention should also be given to his shooting partner in the mixed event, Tarhan, who images showed adopted an equally casual hand-in-pocket stance, albeit wearing headphones and a visor.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Turkish Sports Minister Osman Askin Bak congratulated Dikec on social media, posting a photo of him recreating his now \\\"legendary pose\\\".\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1908, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"score\": 0.8167092016559128, \"rank\": 0.2234577480602302, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osman_I\", \"score\": 0.8861052612450618, \"rank\": 0.12783322284265952, \"text\": \"Osman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osman_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osman_I\"}, {\"begin\": 1938, \"end\": 1943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Askin\", \"score\": 0.9011860770908806, \"rank\": 0.10964873959623893, \"text\": \"Askin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Askin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Askin\"}, {\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.398231841821777e-18, \"text\": \"Bak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clutching a Turkish flag and their medals, Dikec and Tarhan both celebrated their victory at the Champions Park at the Trocadero complex in Paris on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Turkey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Turkish flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.928052800359487e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the week, a South Korean Olympic sharpshooter who took silver in the women's 10-metre air pistol also went viral.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.980742015263376, \"rank\": 0.019629855011836832, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wearing her black South Korea uniform zipped up to the neck, a baseball hat and wire-rimmed shooting glasses, 31-year-old Kim was almost preternaturally calm in videos showing her and her teammate locking up the top two shooting scores in Paris on Sunday.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2353, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999877661955728, \"rank\": 1.2152266524190365e-05, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.928052800359487e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After her win, a 27-second clip showing Kim with the same ultra-calm manner taking aim, shooting her weapon and checking her record-breaking score went viral.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video, which appears to have been shared first in a Reddit thread, actually shows Kim at the Baku World Cup in May, not in Paris.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2808, \"end\": 2814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reddit\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\"}, {\"begin\": 2838, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 2879, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.928052800359487e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even as social media platform X flagged some posts for sharing the footage out of context, the video continued to spread online alongside images of Kim from Paris.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 3048, \"end\": 3053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.928052800359487e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim was quickly declared \\\"the coldest style star of this year's Games\\\" by style magazine GQ.\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3056, \"end\": 3059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 3145, \"end\": 3147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.540409811580654e-28, \"text\": \"GQ\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first-time Olympian took to the range at the Chateauroux Shooting Centre looking like an ultra-contemporary, sportswear-wearing sci-fi assassin,\\\" GQ said.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3166, \"end\": 3174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999837837096, \"rank\": 1.621281460687468e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3301, \"end\": 3303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.540409811580654e-28, \"text\": \"GQ\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One video post that declared Kim to have \\\"the most main character energy\\\" racked up more than 28 million views in a day.\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3340, \"end\": 3343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The footage has spawned fan art of Kim, multiple edits setting the clip to K-pop music and endless memes, including some discussing her unique \\\"aura\\\".\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim, who is ranked first in the women's 10-metre air pistol and fourth in the 25-metre pistol, will be shooting again this week in Paris.\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3585, \"end\": 3588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 3716, \"end\": 3721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.928052800359487e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Kim, the 25-metre event is actually her speciality - and fans will get to watch her in preliminaries on Friday and the finals the following day.\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3728, \"end\": 3731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am confident all the time.\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 I, Kim Ye-ji, am going to win gold no matter what,\\\" she told reporters.\", \"from\": 3904, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3909, \"end\": 3918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye-ji\", \"score\": 0.9999853198696446, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Ye-ji\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye-ji\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Ye-ji\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kim, who lists her hobbies as \\\"sleeping\\\", told South Korean media that she was looking forward to speaking to her five-year-old daughter after all her events are over.\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 4146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3979, \"end\": 3982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 4032, \"end\": 4038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.980742015263376, \"rank\": 0.019629855011836832, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked what she wants to tell her, Kim said gleefully of her new online notoriety: \\\"I think I have become a bit famous now.\\\"\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4187, \"end\": 4190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1811569752652334e-15, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4322, \"entities\": []}]}"